    "about_us_page": {
        "hero": {
            "title_segments": ["Wh","o a","re ","we?"],
            "description": "The NEIIST team is composed of {count} students from Instituto Superior Técnico, motivated and interested in helping all students in their institution who are interested in the most diverse areas of Computer Science. Founded in 2004, all NEIIST members contribute with their effort, dedication and time to organize a wide variety of activities aimed at assisting the academic community to have the best possible academic journey and benefit. Our goal is to foster interest in Computer Science and related areas, promoting contact between students, professors, professionals and companies, as well as organizing activities that contribute to the technical, scientific and human growth of the student community. Our vision is to be a reference in supporting and integrating students from the Department of Informatics Engineering, driving innovation, collaboration and excellence in the teaching and practice of Informatics Engineering.",
